29:26.136 --> 29:27.804
You don't have to check on me. I'm fine.

29:27.888 --> 29:28.921
I'm not.

29:28.972 --> 29:30.923
I needed fresh ice...

29:30.974 --> 29:33.810
For my cocktail.

29:39.987 --> 29:43.466
Jump, jump, jump.

29:47.108 --> 29:47.928
What's up?

29:48.709 --> 29:50.960
Damn, it's cold.

29:51.044 --> 29:53.112
Anybody seen my coat?

30:39.203 --> 30:43.222
Bear!

30:43.290 --> 30:45.658
Do you think it's hibernating?

30:45.709 --> 30:48.428
Nah. I think it's just passed out.

30:48.495 --> 30:51.097
Okay, here's what you're gonna do.

30:51.164 --> 30:54.133
Take this ski pole and jab it real hard.

30:54.184 --> 30:55.852
I don't want to hurt it.

30:55.936 --> 30:57.687
It's too dumb to get hurt.

30:57.771 --> 30:58.938
Trust me. Go ahead.

31:01.391 --> 31:02.742
Ow! Son of a...

31:02.810 --> 31:03.810
It talks!

31:10.067 --> 31:12.184
Aw, man.

31:20.711 --> 31:22.044
You leaving?

31:22.112 --> 31:25.331
Yeah. Thought I'd fly to Denver.

31:25.382 --> 31:27.166
What's in Denver?

31:27.234 --> 31:29.335
My parents.

31:29.386 --> 31:31.604
We need to talk.

31:31.672 --> 31:34.624
I think that's a really good idea.

31:36.126 --> 31:37.994
I hope so.

