Alice Whitehead?

31:52.109 --> 31:54.727
That's a horrible name.

31:54.778 --> 31:56.846
Shut up.

31:56.914 --> 32:00.183
Anyway, I guess we all have our secrets.

32:02.419 --> 32:05.721
Believe it or not, I'm
really gonna miss you.

32:14.748 --> 32:16.999
I'm gonna miss you, too...

32:17.067 --> 32:18.134
Alice.

33:42.636 --> 33:44.336
It's pretty magical, isn't it?

33:44.388 --> 33:46.272
It's so beautiful.

33:46.339 --> 33:48.608
This whole trip has been perfect.

33:49.218 --> 33:51.269
Well, I have to admit,
I had a little help.

33:51.354 --> 33:54.072
Last night at the bar, Jamie
gave me a gold star for luck.

33:54.157 --> 33:55.657
You want to see it?

33:55.725 --> 33:56.942
Yeah.

34:00.663 --> 34:02.013
Oh, wait... that's not it.

34:02.081 --> 34:04.282
That's the engagement ring I got for you.

34:04.367 --> 34:05.867
Where did I put that thing?

34:13.592 --> 34:16.578
Everyone says that the next thing I do,

34:16.629 --> 34:20.031
the next choice I make
is going to define me...

34:20.099 --> 34:23.702
my career... my life.

34:23.768 --> 34:25.353
Well...

34:25.420 --> 34:28.089
The next thing I want to
do is ask you to be my wife

34:28.157 --> 34:31.342
and tell you how much I love you

34:31.409 --> 34:34.312
and how nothing else matters.

34:34.380 --> 34:37.449
When I look into your eyes, Brooke,

34:37.533 --> 34:40.235
I see the rest of my life.

34:40.286 --> 34:42.904
And I see it with you.

34:50.129 --> 34:53.697
Marry me, Brooke Davis.

34:53.766 --> 34:56.351
Yes. Okay.

34:56.418 --> 34:58.920
I want to so much.

34:58.971 --> 35:02.173
I was hoping you were gonna say that.

35:15.538 --> 35:17.572
Come here.

35:17.640 --> 35:19.424
Oh, mom, you're squishing me.

35:19.492 --> 35:21.976
Oh, I'm sorry for squishing you.

35:22.028 --> 35:23.778
Let's go sledding. Do you want to?

35:23.829 --> 35:25.813
- Totally. I'll go tell everyone.
- Okay.

35:25.865 --> 35:27.949
- Dad, we're going sledding!
- All right.

35:32.438 --> 35:34.089
You okay?

35:34.156 --> 35:36.041
No.

35:36.125 --> 35:38.326
But... I will be.

36:14.680 --> 36:16.898
What do you think, Calvin?
It's a long way down.

36:18.751 --> 36:21.920
Piece of cake, Hobbes. Let's do this.

37:29.922 --> 37:33.925
