37:33.993 --> 37:36.294
No, it's just a hill.

37:36.379 --> 37:37.912
Come on.

37:37.980 --> 37:40.114
We'll climb it together.

37:59.968 --> 38:02.137
You know, I don't think
you're actually supposed to

38:02.204 --> 38:03.738
replace stuff in your hotel room.

38:03.806 --> 38:06.658
