out of here soon, anyway.

38:06.742 --> 38:08.576
Think I might get a place of my own...

38:08.644 --> 38:10.945
maybe stick around a while.

38:12.114 --> 38:15.116
Sounds kind of normal and stable.

38:15.167 --> 38:16.951
There.

38:19.121 --> 38:20.755
Perfect.

38:20.823 --> 38:21.756
Well...

38:21.824 --> 38:23.675
almost.

38:23.743 --> 38:25.794
Say you'll go out with
me, and then it will be.

38:30.683 --> 38:32.150
Okay.

38:32.218 --> 38:33.518
Yes.

38:55.174 --> 38:57.542
You know what I like best about the movie?

38:57.626 --> 38:59.344
What's that?

39:01.864 --> 39:06.501
You get the sense that they're
all gonna live happily ever after.

39:08.721 --> 39:10.672
They are.

39:27.306 --> 39:28.356
You okay?

39:30.326 --> 39:33.411
These aren't sad tears.
They're happy tears.

39:33.496 --> 39:36.431
All right, well, how about from now on,

39:36.499 --> 39:38.817
