39:40.402 --> 39:41.853
What is it?

39:45.073 --> 39:46.908
I'm pregnant.

39:48.844 --> 39:51.513
I think it's gonna be a girl.

39:53.916 --> 39:54.883
Oh, my...

40:00.122 --> 40:01.422
Nice work, daddy.

40:14.954 --> 40:17.105
You're falling asleep.
Why don't you go to bed?

40:18.324 --> 40:20.592
I like it here.

40:20.659 --> 40:23.161
Yeah, I like it here, too.

40:23.229 --> 40:26.714
But you sleep like a rock,
and you're too long to carry.

40:26.782 --> 40:27.715
